model.name: Green2024 - whole-body vitamin A metabolism in humans

notes.p: "Use of Population-Based Compartmental Modeling and Retinol Isotope Dilution to Study Vitamin A Kinetics and Total Body Stores Among Ghanaian Women of Reproductive Age" by Mike Green and friends (2024)
The original model was coded in WinSAAM. There the delay compartments were modelled as a series of connected pseudo-compartments. We use the same approach here.
